lbColor 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.5) 
Description: Returns the text color of the item with the given index of the listbox 
 or combobox with id idc of the topmost user dialog. 
The color is returned in format Color.  
Syntax:  
lbColor [idc, index] 
Parameters: 
[idc, index]: Array 
idc: Number of control 
index: Number 
Return Value: 
 Array - format Color